{"tid":465212,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"會員雞絲癲神（舊名滴螺絲）被人起咗底","createTime":"2017-11-11T10:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T05:15:25.000Z","uid":20816,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"1615c892e6b136331e1d1f074530bbf139216c91","tid":465212,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:07:26.000Z","msg":"真名：Matthew Lau<br />\nig: littleeason<br />\nfb: littleeason"},{"pid":"0e32bd05b6c1679e314f15ee3706ac21a9a963a0","tid":465212,"uid":141421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:17:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93d77ca9a6afa343a4e0b234572841ff72ebcd7","tid":465212,"uid":65612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:22:44.000Z","msg":"咩水"},{"pid":"68976b043c2722c8c15caf88bf9f10a88a12c905","tid":465212,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T10:25:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今時今日有咩防中可以同簡迪比較<br />\n<br />\n車仔一冇kante隊波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係當今世界又好似冇咩防中可以同佢相比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比較接近嘅話，之前嘅馬迪賣走左<br />\n卡斯美路成日犯規<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雲耶馬唔會放比車仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底我軌可唔可以搵到一個簡迪嘅替身？搵唔到，今年要拎盃應該凍過水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/464794/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/464794/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"4b87cbbe5706dd31c6460919f0f4fc508621f841","tid":465212,"uid":36497,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T11:39:11.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩 <br />\n無人想知"},{"pid":"47f277fd0db343c9ead5c506902ffdd944b231b5","tid":465212,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T11:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關我撚事咩 <br />\n無人想知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n車迷喎"},{"pid":"f50262f121bd05a1b34fab5088ff4cfe85d35185","tid":465212,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T11:50:52.000Z","msg":"who"},{"pid":"ab678da34de94aa1d8122094bc440eba9aad8d88","tid":465212,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T11:51:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>who</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e4e5e7ac644b61d5a2382b219e6eee94df2367","tid":465212,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T11:53:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>關我撚事咩 <br />\n無人想知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n車迷喎</blockquote><br />\n我都係車迷，你洗唔洗起我底？"},{"pid":"e2702e1e84777a4f018d390de891fdd3833596fe","tid":465212,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T11:56:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>關我撚事咩 <br />\n無人想知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n車迷喎</blockquote><br />\n我都係車迷，你洗唔洗起我底？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7b9d5ab6d0e999cbd56abfe7bbcd9a14860d56","tid":465212,"uid":129521,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T12:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/11/200917_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F11%2F200917_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0f3f7f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" clas